  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t突然发现这个前些天的对话，感慨大陆匪域，嘴敛口抿不敢说话谈吐的龟缩隐忍痛苦模样：<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>专制暴政下中国</b><br/>\n<b>万马齐喑嘴哆嗦</b><br/>\n<b>谁敢直言真笔墨</b><br/>\n<b>文字狱里命蹉跎</b>。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n估计现在共匪大陆土匪窝五毛放屁都要报告填写申请表备案防止恶意放屁：《<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\"><b>中华人民共和国放屁法</b></a>》<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS83MjIzcUlmLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/7223qIf.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7223qIf.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7223qIf.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS85Z2I3NWxSLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/9gb75lR.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9gb75lR.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9gb75lR.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9KM3kxdVFLLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/J3y1uQK.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/J3y1uQK.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J3y1uQK.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\"><b>乱世笑林</b></a> </div>",
